===Noun===
{{en-noun|cold days in Hell}}

# {{lb|en|idiomatic|slang}} The time of occurrence of an event that will never happen.
#: ''It'll be '''a cold day in hell''' when that happens.''

#: "It will be '''a cold day in Hell''' before Sigma Chi at WSU will install bidet's in thier fraternity toilets.''

